Family Model Letter document at the FCC says:
:Model: JHR-AC836M, JHR-AC846M, JHR-AC856M, JHR-AC866M, JHR-AC876M, JHR-AC886M, JHR-AC860M, JHR-AC945M, JHR-AC946M :All the models are the same circuit and RF module, except the model names and colours
Chip IDs are not legible in the FCC photos. Some information derived from [https://baijia.baidu.com/s?old_id=564873 here].
